                                </h3>
                                <div class="mt-4">
                                    <form id="addRoleForm" class="space-y-5">
                                        <div>
                                            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">Vai trò</label>
                                            <select name="roleName" class="block w-full px-4 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 sm:text-sm dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 transition duration-200" required>
